divs: Sighting Detailsi went out side with my fiancia and i look up to the sky like i always do and i notice a light moving in the sky heading south west so i went in side and got my fiancia to come look, then 2 more lights appeard in the sky following each other and were heading west. then the first ufo got real bright then went to its original lighting and kept heading on. then a light streaked across the the sky with fire behind it heading south west. we both freaked out and ran inside.
